name: Domain of Blessing: Sacred Vault IV
description:
A vault that once held the sparks of an ancient civilization, now taken over by villains seeking sacred relics along with the owls of the bedeviled skies.
If you repel the infesting monsters with the blessing of moonlight, you might be rewarded valuable artifacts.

rewardPreview.name: A Day Carved From Rising Winds
A Day Carved From Rising Winds

disorder: After a character triggers a Lunar-Charged, Lunar-Crystallize, or Lunar-Bloom reaction, all party members gain a 35% increase to Lunar-Charged, Lunar-Crystallize, and Lunar-Bloom DMG, as well as a 30% increase to DEF, for 10s.
